{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"ispaid":1,"exhibit_id":"XMT_lsnz","exhibition_name":"展览二区","location":"507,812","name":"老少年轴","size":"晚清民国 纵108cm，横50cm","like":0,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=91","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=XMT_lsnz","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"","description":"吴昌硕，1844年至1927年，原名俊，字昌硕，别号缶庐、苦铁等，汉族，浙江湖州人。中国近、现代书画艺术发展过渡时期的关键人物，“诗、书、画、印”四绝的一代宗师，晚清民国时期著名国画家、书法家、篆刻家，与任伯年、蒲华、虚谷齐名为“清末海派四大家”。吴昌硕的艺术另辟蹊径、贵于创造，最擅长写意花卉，他以书法入画，把书法、篆刻的行笔、运刀、章法融入绘画，形成富有金石味的独特画风。他以篆笔写梅兰，狂草作葡萄，所作花卉木石，笔力敦厚老辣、纵横恣肆、气势雄强，形成强烈的画面对比感。","images":["content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/pslKvpB0B_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/pslKvpB0B1_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/pslKvpB0B2_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/pslKvpB0B3_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/image/pslKvpB0B4_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/xmt_museum/audio/xWibY68lyu.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""}}}